  "content_html": "<div class=\"rich-text\"><h3 class=\"font_3 wixui-rich-text__text\" dir=\"ltr\" style=\"font-size:30px;\"><span class=\"color_25 wixui-rich-text__text\"><span class=\"wixui-rich-text__text\" style=\"font-weight:bold;\"><span class=\"wixui-rich-text__text\" style=\"font-size:30px;\"><span class=\"wixui-rich-text__text\" style=\"font-family:arial,ｍｓ ｐゴシック,ms pgothic,돋움,dotum,helvetica,sans-serif;\">DigiPoint digital programmable controller</span></span></span></span></h3></div>\n<div class=\"rich-text\"><p class=\"font_8 wixui-rich-text__text\" dir=\"ltr\" style=\"font-size:18px;\"><span class=\"wixui-rich-text__text\" style=\"font-size:18px;\"><span class=\"wixui-rich-text__text\" style=\"font-family:arial,ｍｓ ｐゴシック,ms pgothic,돋움,dotum,helvetica,sans-serif;\">DigiPoint is an independent controller that includes an internal clock that can be programmed using a ladder diagram and software routines developed for different uses, the controller was specially designed for controlling and monitoring lighting systems and electromechanical systems in public and industrial buildings.</span></span></p>\n<p class=\"font_8 wixui-rich-text__text\" dir=\"ltr\" style=\"font-size:18px;\"><span class=\"wixui-rich-text__text\" style=\"font-size:18px;\"><span class=\"wixui-rich-text__text\" style=\"font-family:arial,ｍｓ ｐゴシック,ms pgothic,돋움,dotum,helvetica,sans-serif;\"><span class=\"wixGuard wixui-rich-text__text\">​</span></span></span></p>\n<p class=\"font_8 wixui-rich-text__text\" dir=\"ltr\" style=\"font-size:18px;\"><span class=\"wixui-rich-text__text\" style=\"font-size:18px;\"><span class=\"wixui-rich-text__text\" style=\"font-family:arial,ｍｓ ｐゴシック,ms pgothic,돋움,dotum,helvetica,sans-serif;\">The controller is specially adapted for hotels, office buildings, hospitals, universities, museums, clean industry and more.</span></span></p>\n<p class=\"font_8 wixui-rich-text__text\" dir=\"ltr\" style=\"font-size:18px;\"><span class=\"wixui-rich-text__text\" style=\"font-size:18px;\"><span class=\"wixui-rich-text__text\" style=\"font-family:arial,ｍｓ ｐゴシック,ms pgothic,돋움,dotum,helvetica,sans-serif;\"><span class=\"wixGuard wixui-rich-text__text\">​</span></span></span></p>\n<p class=\"font_8 wixui-rich-text__text\" dir=\"ltr\" style=\"font-size:18px;\"><span class=\"wixui-rich-text__text\" style=\"font-size:18px;\"><span class=\"wixui-rich-text__text\" style=\"font-family:arial,ｍｓ ｐゴシック,ms pgothic,돋움,dotum,helvetica,sans-serif;\">The controller enables easy, efficient and quick programming, and includes open and accepted communication protocols such as:</span></span></p>\n<p class=\"font_8 wixui-rich-text__text\" dir=\"ltr\" style=\"font-size:18px;\"><span class=\"wixui-rich-text__text\" style=\"font-size:18px;\"><span class=\"wixui-rich-text__text\" style=\"font-family:arial,ｍｓ ｐゴシック,ms pgothic,돋움,dotum,helvetica,sans-serif;\">Modbus RTU + IP as well as BACnet IP + MSTP.</span></span></p>\n<p class=\"font_8 wixui-rich-text__text\" dir=\"ltr\" style=\"font-size:18px;\"><span class=\"wixui-rich-text__text\" style=\"font-size:18px;\"><span class=\"wixui-rich-text__text\" style=\"font-family:arial,ｍｓ ｐゴシック,ms pgothic,돋움,dotum,helvetica,sans-serif;\"><span class=\"wixGuard wixui-rich-text__text\">​</span></span></span></p>\n<p class=\"font_8 wixui-rich-text__text\" dir=\"ltr\" style=\"font-size:18px;\"><span class=\"wixui-rich-text__text\" style=\"font-size:18px;\"><span class=\"wixui-rich-text__text\" style=\"font-family:arial,ｍｓ ｐゴシック,ms pgothic,돋움,dotum,helvetica,sans-serif;\">The controller enables the reading of fast pulses and their production (for stock systems) as well as the ability to surf to it via a browser.</span></span></p>\n<p class=\"font_8 wixui-rich-text__text\" dir=\"ltr\" style=\"font-size:18px;\"><span class=\"wixui-rich-text__text\" style=\"font-size:18px;\"><span class=\"wixui-rich-text__text\" style=\"font-family:arial,ｍｓ ｐゴシック,ms pgothic,돋움,dotum,helvetica,sans-serif;\"><span class=\"wixGuard wixui-rich-text__text\">​</span></span></span></p>\n<p class=\"font_8 wixui-rich-text__text\" dir=\"ltr\" style=\"font-size:18px;\"><span class=\"wixui-rich-text__text\" style=\"font-size:18px;\"><span class=\"wixui-rich-text__text\" style=\"font-family:arial,ｍｓ ｐゴシック,ms pgothic,돋움,dotum,helvetica,sans-serif;\">These capabilities make the DigiPoint controller a very attractive controller both as an independent controller and as an expansion card for the Veropoint controller.</span></span></p></div>\n<div class=\"rich-text\"><h3 class=\"font_3 wixui-rich-text__text\" dir=\"ltr\" style=\"font-size:40px;\"><span class=\"wixui-rich-text__text\" style=\"font-weight:bold;\"><span style=\"font-family:arial,ｍｓ ｐゴシック,ms pgothic,돋\">움,dotum,helvetica,sans-serif;\" class=\"wixui-rich-text__text\"&gt;Related Products</span></span></h3></div>\n<div class=\"rich-text\"><p class=\"font_7 wixui-rich-text__text\" style=\"font-size:22px; text-align:center;\"><span class=\"wixui-rich-text__text\" style=\"font-size:22px;\"><span class=\"wixui-rich-text__text\" style=\"font-weight:bold;\"><span class=\"wixui-rich-text__text\" style=\"font-family:arial,ｍｓ ｐゴシック,ms pgothic,돋움,dotum,helvetica,sans-serif;\"><span class=\"wixui-rich-text__text\" style=\"color:#FFFFFF;\">Control Applications Ltd</span></span></span></span></p></div>\n<div class=\"rich-text\"><p class=\"font_7 wixui-rich-text__text\" style=\"font-size:20px;\"><span class=\"wixui-rich-text__text\" style=\"font-weight:bold;\"><span class=\"wixui-rich-text__text\" style=\"font-size:20px;\"><span class=\"wixui-rich-text__text\" style=\"font-family:arial,ｍｓ ｐゴシック,ms pgothic,돋움,dotum,helvetica,sans-serif;\"><span class=\"wixui-rich-text__text\" style=\"color:#FFFFFF;\">making contact</span></span></span></span></p>\n<p class=\"font_7 wixui-rich-text__text\" dir=\"ltr\" style=\"font-size:20px; text-align:left;\"><span class=\"wixui-rich-text__text\" style=\"color:rgb(255, 255, 255); font-family:arial,ｍｓ ｐゴシック,ms pgothic,돋움,dotum,helvetica,sans-serif; font