  "rich_text": [
    "DigiPoint digital programmable controller",
    "DigiPoint is an independent controller that includes an internal clock that can be programmed using a ladder diagram and software routines developed for different uses, the controller was specially designed for controlling and monitoring lighting systems and electromechanical systems in public and industrial buildings.\n​\nThe controller is specially adapted for hotels, office buildings, hospitals, universities, museums, clean industry and more.\n​\nThe controller enables easy, efficient and quick programming, and includes open and accepted communication protocols such as:\nModbus RTU + IP as well as BACnet IP + MSTP.\n​\nThe controller enables the reading of fast pulses and their production (for stock systems) as well as the ability to surf to it via a browser.\n​\nThese capabilities make the DigiPoint controller a very attractive controller both as an independent controller and as an expansion card for the Veropoint controller.",
    "Related Products",
    "Control Applications Ltd",
    "making contact\nPhone: +972-3-6474998\n​\nFax: +972-3-6474598\nEmail:\ncal@ddc.co.il",
    "opening hours\nControl Applications Ltd\nSunday - Thursday\n08:00 - 17:00",
    "Address\n25 Barzel Street, Tel Aviv\n6971035\nIsrael",
    "© Copyright - Control Applications Ltd"
  ],
